<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_400_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Jobs pelers <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l4">das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu als wır Jm nehſt ʒuſagen lıeſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l5">ob er in xıııȷ <expan>tag<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu Vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . daʒ er denn geleyt ſölt ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l6">habt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Alſo <expan>erleng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wır Jm das vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wıllen / Wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_400_r1l7">er <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> des <expan>nehſt<ex>en</ex></expan> ſunntags <expan>vb<ex>er</ex></expan> xıııȷ tag ʒu vns kombt ſo </ab>
